PrecisAppointment of MELVIN CAPPE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure; designation of MELVIN CAPPE as Deputy Minister of Labour; and appointment of MELVIN CAPPE as commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Chairperson of the Commission.
